Toolbar Position Changer v0.2.8 (released 2016-09-09)
    -  Fix duplicate toolbars in Waterfox hide/show toolbar menu.
       
Toolbar Position Changer v0.2.7 (released 2016-08-28)
    -  Fix bright icon theme not loading for bottom toolbars.
    -  Fix navbar toolbar color in customize view.
    -  Change toolbar options to inline options.
    -  Change to use nsIDOMWindowUtils to load style sheets.
       
Toolbar Position Changer v0.2.6 (released 2016-08-23)
    -  Fix two compatibility problems with CTR addon: main menu not opening and
       showing some duplicate toolbars in show/hide toolbars menu.

